{"tid":264923,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] Pocket Morty","createTime":"2017-05-31T08:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T12:25:17.000Z","uid":63610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8654df2a413cdcdeb61481bcdb8e4c2a856f89b8","tid":264923,"uid":63610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:44:09.000Z","msg":"美國Adult Swim出嘅神級動畫Rick and Morty連登就比較少討論<br />\n因為publicity始終都唔好<br />\n簡單講就係用好有創意嘅手法去explore existential nihilism (存在虛無主義)<br />\n有興趣可以去 gomovies都search吓<br />\n<br />\n講番隻game<br />\nPocket Morty係模仿同諷刺pokemon嘅<br />\n遊戲入面rick會收集唔同種類嘅mortys去同其他dimensiom嘅rick對戰<br />\n單機版上年出<br />\n遊戲目標係打底所有其他dimensiom嘅rick同counsel<br />\n最後就係收集所有morty<br />\n<br />\n至於multiplayer封測就喺今個月月頭出<br />\nandroid先有<br />\n詳情可以參考官方twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/pocketmortys/status/861976396700286976?lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fpocketmortys%2Fstatus%2F861976396700286976%3Flang%3Den&d=jl7n1qwn2WWIzNfmHyC6m6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ecff8ad3\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/pocketmortys/status/861976396700286976?lang=en</a><br />\n<br />\n主流game玩悶咗建議一路睇動畫一路玩<br />\n好有趣"},{"pid":"6c18eb141abd4f315f55d8d24b74fa317828ce8b","tid":264923,"uid":14272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:38:07.000Z","msg":"冇人有玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebbaf01195ac5c1531e8014d50842aec9c70e9d6","tid":264923,"uid":332610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"岩岩玩"},{"pid":"90a5ca222ba1cc53fe828b4c3cc2e6d1c711cc4c","tid":264923,"uid":8721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:50:15.000Z","msg":"2020 先玩 係咪太遲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccc025aa5304df1a66e46d55f6aa73550f4cd04","tid":264923,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"